# FastX Git Ignore Config

# Core sensitive files & configurations (Secrets)
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/application*.properties

# Docker configurations
**/Dockerfile
**/dockerfile
**/docker-compose.yml
**/docker-compose.yaml

# UML Diagrams & database seed/schema files
**/*.puml
**/*.sql

# Security keys / PEM files
**/*.pem

# Java build and IDE files
**/target/
**/.idea/
**/.settings/
**/.metadata/
**/*.class
**/*.jar
**/*.war
**/*.ear
**/.classpath
**/.project
**/.factorypath
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak

# Node / Frontend build and dependencies
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/dist-ssr/
**/*.local
**/.vscode/
**/.DS_Store
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*
